name: Rip It Up / Shake, Rattle and Roll / Blue Suede Shoes
comments: Although released as a medley on Anthology 3, all three songs were not actually recorded as one. The songs were among a number of rock 'n' roll songs recorded by The Beatles on 26 January.  Rip It Up, which quickly segued into Shake, Rattle And Roll was one take and Blue Suede Shoes was recorded later in the day.
